strings:
<voice_0x01000E04><se_low>*: Whoa-oa-oa! Sounds good!
I knew that it would!

<voice_0x01000E05><se_low>*: Yeah! Papa's got a brand new toy!
This harp makes me sound hotter than ever, baby!

<voice_0x01000E06><se_low>*: All those years tunnelin' to the castle!
But y'all stayed on the scene...like a diggin' machine!

<voice_0x01000E07><se_low>*: Hey, come on, fellas!
What's with the silence? Oh, I get it!
My groove's so hip it's got y'all speechless, huh!?
